{
  "video_id": "sYy-LEdYr8A",
  "title": "Ilona Szab√≥ de Carvalho: 4 lessons I learned from taking a stand against drugs and gun violence",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12817.0,
      "end_time": 14993.0,
      "text": "About 12 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14993.0,
      "end_time": 17245.0,
      "text": "I gave up my career in banking"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17245.0,
      "end_time": 20356.0,
      "text": "to try to make the world a safer place."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20356.0,
      "end_time": 24565.0,
      "text": "This involved a journey into national and global advocacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24565.0,
      "end_time": 29388.0,
      "text": "and meeting some of the most extraordinary people in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29388.0,
      "end_time": 34566.0,
      "text": "In the process, I became a civil society diplomat."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34566.0,
      "end_time": 38720.0,
      "text": "Civil society diplomats do three things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38720.0,
      "end_time": 40603.0,
      "text": "They voice the concerns of the people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40603.0,
      "end_time": 43691.0,
      "text": "are not pinned down by national interests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43691.0,
      "end_time": 46528.0,
      "text": "and influence change through citizen networks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46528.0,
      "end_time": 49830.0,
      "text": "not only state ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49840.0,
      "end_time": 53683.0,
      "text": "And if you want to change the world, we need more of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53683.0,
      "end_time": 56190.0,
      "text": "But many people still ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56190.0,
      "end_time": 60741.0,
      "text": "\"Can civil society really make a big difference?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60741.0,
      "end_time": 66120.0,
      "text": "Can citizens influence and shape national and global policy?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66120.0,
      "end_time": 68961.0,
      "text": "I never thought I would ask myself these questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68961.0,
      "end_time": 72211.0,
      "text": "but here I am to share some lessons"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 72211.0,
      "end_time": 77227.0,
      "text": "about two powerful civil society  movements that I&#39;ve been involved in."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77227.0,
      "end_time": 81350.0,
      "text": "They are in issues that I&#39;m passionate about:"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81350.0,
      "end_time": 85214.0,
      "text": "gun control and drug policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 85214.0,
      "end_time": 88859.0,
      "text": "And these are issues that matter here."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 88859.0,
      "end_time": 94253.0,
      "text": "Latin America is ground zero for both of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 94253.0,
      "end_time": 96296.0,
      "text": "For example, Brazil --"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96296.0,
      "end_time": 102550.0,
      "text": "this beautiful country hosting TEDGlobal has the world&#39;s ugliest record."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 102550.0,
      "end_time": 108448.0,
      "text": "We are the number one champion in homicidal violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 108448.0,
      "end_time": 114564.0,
      "text": "One in every 10 people killed around the world is a Brazilian."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 114569.0,
      "end_time": 119678.0,
      "text": "This translates into over 56,000 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 119678.0,
      "end_time": 123161.0,
      "text": "dying violently each year."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 123161.0,
      "end_time": 129820.0,
      "text": "Most of them are young, black boys dying by guns."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 129820.0,
      "end_time": 134213.0,
      "text": "Brazil is also one of the world&#39;s largest consumers of drugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 134213.0,
      "end_time": 139660.0,
      "text": "and the War on Drugs has been especially painful here."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 139660.0,
      "end_time": 142339.0,
      "text": "Around 50 percent of the homicides in the streets in Brazil"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 142339.0,
      "end_time": 145776.0,
      "text": "are related to the War on Drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 145776.0,
      "end_time": 151464.0,
      "text": "The same is true for about 25 percent of people in jail."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 151464.0,
      "end_time": 156596.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just Brazil that is affected by the twin problems of guns and drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 156596.0,
      "end_time": 163620.0,
      "text": "Virtually every country and city across Central and South America is in trouble."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 163620.0,
      "end_time": 167869.0,
      "text": "Latin America has nine percent of the world&#39;s population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 167869.0,
      "end_time": 172930.0,
      "text": "but 25 percent of its global violent deaths."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 172930.0,
      "end_time": 175972.0,
      "text": "These are not problems we can run away from."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 175972.0,
      "end_time": 178271.0,
      "text": "I certainly could not."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 178271.0,
      "end_time": 183147.0,
      "text": "So the first campaign I got involved with started here in 2003"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 183147.0,
      "end_time": 185190.0,
      "text": "to change Brazil&#39;s gun law"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 185190.0,
      "end_time": 188278.0,
      "text": "and to create a program to buy back weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 188278.0,
      "end_time": 189857.0,
      "text": "In just a few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 189857.0,
      "end_time": 192295.0,
      "text": "we not only changed national legislation"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 192295.0,
      "end_time": 196330.0,
      "text": "that made it much more difficult for civilians to buy a gun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 196330.0,
      "end_time": 201683.0,
      "text": "but we collected and destroyed almost half a million weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 201683.0,
      "end_time": 206262.0,
      "text": "This was one of the biggest buyback programs in history --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 206262.0,
      "end_time": 208921.0,
      "text": "(Applause) --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 208921.0,
      "end_time": 212542.0,
      "text": "but we also suffered some setbacks."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 212542.0,
      "end_time": 218324.0,
      "text": "We lost a referendum to ban gun sales to civilians in 2005."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 218324.0,
      "end_time": 221597.0,
      "text": "The second initiative was also home-grown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 221597.0,
      "end_time": 227147.0,
      "text": "but is today a global movement to reform the international drug control regime."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 227147.0,
      "end_time": 228938.0,
      "text": "I am the executive coordinator"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 228938.0,
      "end_time": 233416.0,
      "text": "of something called the Global Commission on Drug Policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 233416.0,
      "end_time": 235853.0,
      "text": "The commission is a high-level group"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 235854.0,
      "end_time": 239755.0,
      "text": "of global leaders brought together to identify more humane"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 239755.0,
      "end_time": 243911.0,
      "text": "and effective approaches to the issue of drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 243911.0,
      "end_time": 248479.0,
      "text": "Since we started in 2008, the taboo on drugs is broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 248479.0,
      "end_time": 253431.0,
      "text": "Across the Americas, from the US and Mexico to Colombia and Uruguay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 253431.0,
      "end_time": 255579.0,
      "text": "change is in the air."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 255579.0,
      "end_time": 259381.0,
      "text": "But rather than tell you the whole story about these two movements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 259380.0,
      "end_time": 263188.0,
      "text": "I just want to share with you four key insights."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 263189.0,
      "end_time": 266788.0,
      "text": "I call them lessons to change the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 266788.0,
      "end_time": 269170.0,
      "text": "There are certainly many more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 269170.0,
      "end_time": 272314.0,
      "text": "but these are the ones that stand out to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 272314.0,
      "end_time": 274496.0,
      "text": "So the first lesson is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 274496.0,
      "end_time": 277770.0,
      "text": "Change and control the narrative."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 277770.0,
      "end_time": 279604.0,
      "text": "It may seem obvious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 279604.0,
      "end_time": 282645.0,
      "text": "but a key ingredient to civil society diplomacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 282646.0,
      "end_time": 286733.0,
      "text": "is first changing and then controlling the narrative."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 286733.0,
      "end_time": 289890.0,
      "text": "This is something that veteran politicians understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 289890.0,
      "end_time": 294813.0,
      "text": "but that civil society groups generally do not do very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 294813.0,
      "end_time": 297158.0,
      "text": "In the case of drug policy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 297158.0,
      "end_time": 300618.0,
      "text": "our biggest success has been to change the discussion"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 300618.0,
      "end_time": 303427.0,
      "text": "away from prosecuting a War on Drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 303427.0,
      "end_time": 307398.0,
      "text": "to putting people&#39;s health and safety first."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 307398.0,
      "end_time": 310834.0,
      "text": "In a cutting-edge report we just launched in New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 310834.0,
      "end_time": 318403.0,
      "text": "we also showed that the groups benefiting most from this $320 billion market"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 318403.0,
      "end_time": 321724.0,
      "text": "are criminal gangs and cartels."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 321724.0,
      "end_time": 325462.0,
      "text": "So in order to undermine the power and profit of these groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 325462.0,
      "end_time": 328433.0,
      "text": "we need to change the conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 328434.0,
      "end_time": 334726.0,
      "text": "We need to make illegal drugs legal."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 334726.0,
      "end_time": 337559.0,
      "text": "But before I get you too excited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 337559.0,
      "end_time": 340694.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t mean drugs should be a free-for-all."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 340702.0,
      "end_time": 344827.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m talking about, and what the Global Commission advocates for"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 344827.0,
      "end_time": 349354.0,
      "text": "is creating a highly regulated market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 349354.0,
      "end_time": 354579.0,
      "text": "where different drugs would have different degrees of regulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 354579.0,
      "end_time": 358619.0,
      "text": "As for gun control, we were successful in changing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 358619.0,
      "end_time": 361544.0,
      "text": "but not so much in controlling, the narrative."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 361544.0,
      "end_time": 364400.0,
      "text": "And this brings me to my next lesson:"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 364400.0,
      "end_time": 368323.0,
      "text": "Never underestimate your opponents."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 368324.0,
      "end_time": 370553.0,
      "text": "If you want to succeed in changing the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 370553.0,
      "end_time": 372922.0,
      "text": "you need to know who you&#39;re up against."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 372922.0,
      "end_time": 376590.0,
      "text": "You need to learn their motivations and points of view."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 376590.0,
      "end_time": 378796.0,
      "text": "In the case of gun control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 378796.0,
      "end_time": 382349.0,
      "text": "we really underestimated our opponents."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 382349.0,
      "end_time": 385274.0,
      "text": "After a very successful gun-collection program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 385274.0,
      "end_time": 386618.0,
      "text": "we were elated."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 386618.0,
      "end_time": 389454.0,
      "text": "We had support from 80 percent of Brazilians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 389454.0,
      "end_time": 392335.0,
      "text": "and thought that this could help us win the referendum"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 392335.0,
      "end_time": 394746.0,
      "text": "to ban gun sales to civilians."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 394747.0,
      "end_time": 397928.0,
      "text": "But we were dead wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 397928.0,
      "end_time": 401249.0,
      "text": "During a televised 20-day public debate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 401249.0,
      "end_time": 405103.0,
      "text": "our opponent used our own arguments against us."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 405103.0,
      "end_time": 407332.0,
      "text": "We ended up losing the popular vote."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 407332.0,
      "end_time": 409677.0,
      "text": "It was really terrible."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 409677.0,
      "end_time": 415836.0,
      "text": "The National Rifle Association -- yes, the American NRA --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 415836.0,
      "end_time": 417595.0,
      "text": "came to Brazil."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 417595.0,
      "end_time": 420695.0,
      "text": "They inundated our campaign with their propaganda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 420695.0,
      "end_time": 422238.0,
      "text": "that as you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 422238.0,
      "end_time": 426581.0,
      "text": "links the right to own guns to ideas of freedom and democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 426581.0,
      "end_time": 430458.0,
      "text": "They simply threw everything at us."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 430458.0,
      "end_time": 432385.0,
      "text": "They used our national flag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 432385.0,
      "end_time": 434800.0,
      "text": "our independence anthem."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 434800.0,
      "end_time": 435914.0,
      "text": "They invoked women&#39;s rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 435915.0,
      "end_time": 441302.0,
      "text": "and misused images of Mandela, Tiananmen Square, and even Hitler."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 441302.0,
      "end_time": 445272.0,
      "text": "They won by playing with people&#39;s fears."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 445272.0,
      "end_time": 449916.0,
      "text": "In fact, guns were almost completely ignored in their campaign."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 449916.0,
      "end_time": 453213.0,
      "text": "Their focus was on individual rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 453213.0,
      "end_time": 454792.0,
      "text": "But I ask you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 454792.0,
      "end_time": 457200.0,
      "text": "which right is more important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 457210.0,
      "end_time": 458832.0,
      "text": "the right to life"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 458832.0,
      "end_time": 461897.0,
      "text": "or the right to have a gun that takes life away?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 461897.0,
      "end_time": 466150.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 466150.0,
      "end_time": 469972.0,
      "text": "We thought people would vote in defense of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 469972.0,
      "end_time": 474756.0,
      "text": "but in a country with a recent past of military dictatorship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 474756.0,
      "end_time": 479270.0,
      "text": "the anti-government message of our opponents resonated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 479270.0,
      "end_time": 482626.0,
      "text": "and we were not prepared to respond."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 482626.0,
      "end_time": 484715.0,
      "text": "Lesson learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 484715.0,
      "end_time": 488500.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been more successful in the case of drug policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 488500.0,
      "end_time": 492719.0,
      "text": "If you asked most people 10 years ago if an end to the War on Drugs was possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 492719.0,
      "end_time": 494731.0,
      "text": "they would have laughed."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 494731.0,
      "end_time": 498229.0,
      "text": "After all, there are huge military police prisons"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 498229.0,
      "end_time": 502325.0,
      "text": "and financial establishments benefiting from this war."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 502325.0,
      "end_time": 508970.0,
      "text": "But today, the international drug control regime is starting to crumble."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 508970.0,
      "end_time": 512925.0,
      "text": "Governments and civil societies are experimenting with new approaches."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 512926.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515248.00000000006,
      "text": "The Global Commission on Drug Policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 515248.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517315.00000000006,
      "text": "really knew its opposition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 517315.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519149.00000000006,
      "text": "and rather than fighting them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 519149.0,
      "end_time": 523793.0,
      "text": "our chair -- former Brazilian President Fernando Henrique Cardoso --"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 523793.0,
      "end_time": 528650.0,
      "text": "reached out to leaders from across the political spectrum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 528650.0,
      "end_time": 530875.0,
      "text": "from liberals to conservatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 530875.0,
      "end_time": 535751.0,
      "text": "This high level group agreed to honestly discuss"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 535751.0,
      "end_time": 537701.0,
      "text": "the merits and flaws of drug policies."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 537701.0,
      "end_time": 542461.0,
      "text": "It was this reasoned, informed and strategic discussion"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 542461.0,
      "end_time": 546222.0,
      "text": "that revealed the sad truth about the War on Drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 546222.0,
      "end_time": 552538.0,
      "text": "The War on Drugs has simply failed across every metric."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 552538.0,
      "end_time": 555440.0,
      "text": "Drugs are cheaper and more available than ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 555440.0,
      "end_time": 558227.0,
      "text": "and consumption has risen globally."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 558227.0,
      "end_time": 560409.0,
      "text": "But even worse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 560409.0,
      "end_time": 566980.0,
      "text": "it also generated massive negative unintended consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 566980.0,
      "end_time": 570626.0,
      "text": "It is true that some people have made these arguments before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 570626.0,
      "end_time": 572366.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;ve made a difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 572366.0,
      "end_time": 575377.0,
      "text": "by anticipating the arguments of our opponents"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 575378.0,
      "end_time": 577484.0,
      "text": "and by leveraging powerful voices"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 577484.0,
      "end_time": 582374.0,
      "text": "that a few years ago would probably have resisted change."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 582374.0,
      "end_time": 586461.0,
      "text": "Third lesson: Use data to drive your argument."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 586461.0,
      "end_time": 589456.0,
      "text": "Guns and drugs are emotive issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 589456.0,
      "end_time": 593357.0,
      "text": "and as we&#39;ve painfully learned in the gun referendum campaign in Brazil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 593357.0,
      "end_time": 596422.0,
      "text": "sometimes it&#39;s impossible to cut through the emotions"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 596422.0,
      "end_time": 598512.0,
      "text": "and get to the facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 598512.0,
      "end_time": 601599.0,
      "text": "But this doesn&#39;t mean that we shouldn&#39;t try."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 601600.0,
      "end_time": 603251.0,
      "text": "Until quite recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 603251.0,
      "end_time": 607265.0,
      "text": "we simply didn&#39;t know how many Brazilians were killed by guns."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 607265.0,
      "end_time": 612780.0,
      "text": "Amazingly, it was a local soap opera called \"Mulheres Apaixonadas\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 612780.0,
      "end_time": 614497.0,
      "text": "or \"Women in Love\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 614498.0,
      "end_time": 618410.0,
      "text": "that kicked off Brazil&#39;s national gun control campaign."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 618410.0,
      "end_time": 620872.0,
      "text": "In one highly viewed episode,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 620872.0,
      "end_time": 625740.0,
      "text": "a soap opera lead actress was killed by a stray bullet."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 625740.0,
      "end_time": 629370.0,
      "text": "Brazilian grannies and housewives were outraged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 629370.0,
      "end_time": 632644.0,
      "text": "and in a case of art imitating life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 632644.0,
      "end_time": 637938.0,
      "text": "this episode also included footage of a real gun control march"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 637938.0,
      "end_time": 640422.0,
      "text": "that we had organized right here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 640422.0,
      "end_time": 643255.0,
      "text": "outside in Copacabana Beach."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 643255.0,
      "end_time": 648699.0,
      "text": "The televised death and march had a huge impact on public opinion."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 648699.0,
      "end_time": 653483.0,
      "text": "Within weeks, our national congress approved the disarmament bill"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 653483.0,
      "end_time": 656570.0,
      "text": "that had been languishing for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 656571.0,
      "end_time": 659586.0,
      "text": "We were then able to mobilize data"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 659586.0,
      "end_time": 662886.0,
      "text": "to show the successful outcomes of the change in the law"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 662886.0,
      "end_time": 665700.0,
      "text": "and gun collection program."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 665700.0,
      "end_time": 666768.0,
      "text": "Here is what I mean:"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 666769.0,
      "end_time": 670293.0,
      "text": "We could prove that in just one year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 670293.0,
      "end_time": 675990.0,
      "text": "we saved more than 5,000 lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 675990.0,
      "end_time": 678862.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 678862.0,
      "end_time": 681276.0,
      "text": "And in the case of drugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 681276.0,
      "end_time": 686569.0,
      "text": "in order to undermine this fear and prejudice that surrounds the issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 686570.0,
      "end_time": 691678.0,
      "text": "we managed to gather and present data that shows that today&#39;s drug policies"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 691678.0,
      "end_time": 695549.0,
      "text": "cause much more harm than drug use per se,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 695549.0,
      "end_time": 699682.0,
      "text": "and people are starting to get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 699682.0,
      "end_time": 701818.0,
      "text": "My fourth insight is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 701818.0,
      "end_time": 706440.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t be afraid to bring together odd bedfellows."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 706440.0,
      "end_time": 708180.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;ve learned in Brazil --"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 708180.0,
      "end_time": 710363.0,
      "text": "and this doesn&#39;t only apply to my country --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 710363.0,
      "end_time": 714995.0,
      "text": "is the importance of bringing diverse and eclectic folks together."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 714995.0,
      "end_time": 717131.0,
      "text": "If you want to change the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 717131.0,
      "end_time": 721427.0,
      "text": "it helps to have a good cross-section of society on your side."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 721427.0,
      "end_time": 724270.0,
      "text": "In both the case of guns and drugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 724270.0,
      "end_time": 727463.0,
      "text": "we brought together a wonderful mix of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 727463.0,
      "end_time": 731666.0,
      "text": "We mobilized the elite and got huge support from the media."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 731667.0,
      "end_time": 736124.0,
      "text": "We gathered the victims, human rights champions, cultural icons."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 736124.0,
      "end_time": 738701.0,
      "text": "We also assembled the professional classes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 738701.0,
      "end_time": 741697.0,
      "text": "doctors, lawyers, academia and more."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 741697.0,
      "end_time": 744437.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;ve learned over the last years"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 744437.0,
      "end_time": 750337.0,
      "text": "is that you need coalitions of the willing and of the unwilling to make change."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 750337.0,
      "end_time": 752204.0,
      "text": "In the case of drugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 752204.0,
      "end_time": 755790.0,
      "text": "we needed libertarians, anti-prohibitionists, legalizers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 755791.0,
      "end_time": 758136.0,
      "text": "and liberal politicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 758136.0,
      "end_time": 760597.0,
      "text": "They may not agree on everything;"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 760597.0,
      "end_time": 764846.0,
      "text": "in fact, they disagree on almost everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 764846.0,
      "end_time": 770615.0,
      "text": "But the legitimacy of the campaign is based on their diverse points of view."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 771521.0,
      "end_time": 773762.0,
      "text": "Over a decade ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 773762.0,
      "end_time": 778219.0,
      "text": "I had a comfortable future working for an investment bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 778220.0,
      "end_time": 782492.0,
      "text": "I was as far removed from the world of civil society diplomacy"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 782492.0,
      "end_time": 784767.0,
      "text": "as you can imagine."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 784768.0,
      "end_time": 786927.0,
      "text": "But I took a chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 786927.0,
      "end_time": 788924.0,
      "text": "I changed course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 788924.0,
      "end_time": 792284.0,
      "text": "and on the way, I helped  to create social movements"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 792284.0,
      "end_time": 797400.0,
      "text": "that I believe have made  some parts of the world safer."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 797400.0,
      "end_time": 802178.0,
      "text": "Each and every one of us has the power to change the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 802178.0,
      "end_time": 806790.0,
      "text": "No matter what the issue, and no matter how hard the fight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 806790.0,
      "end_time": 811504.0,
      "text": "civil society is central to the blueprint for change."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 811504.0,
      "end_time": 813815.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 813815.0,
      "end_time": 817832.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}